Sorry about that.  Fixed subsequent to 1.6 release.  Here's the CVS 
commit message (Heritrix release is using revision 1.5.0.2. of the 
JmxUtils file).

revision 1.7
date: 2005/12/06 02:18:28;  author: stack-sf;  state: Exp;  lines: +3 -1
Fix '[ 1365804 ] JmxUtils.getOpenType() must handle Doubles'.
* src/java/org/archive/util/JmxUtils.java
    Add handling of doubles.

You might try with the Heritrix HEAD or pull down the 1.7.2 tag, an 
internal release that we know is basically stable.

St.Ack
